ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-out-now-on-switch-and-ps4-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/red-dead-redemption"><em>Red Dead Redemption</em></a>已于今天（8 月 17 日）面向<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/nintendo-switch">Nintendo Switch</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/playstation-4">PlayStation 4</a>发布，其中包含<em>Undead Nightmare</em>扩展包和精选奖励内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/exclusive-bastilles-dan-smith-wants-to-soundtrack-red-dead-redemption-3-3300694">巴士底狱的丹·史密斯希望为《荒野大镖客：救赎 3》配乐</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/red-dead-redemption-coming-to-playstation-5-backwards-compatibility-3479431">本月早些时候宣布</a>，这个版本的<em>Red Dead Redemption</em>是米德尔斯堡开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/double-eleven">Double Eleven</a>的作品。这两款游戏包括<em>年度游戏版</em>的额外内容，如经典战斧、爆炸步枪、金枪武器等。玩家还可以获得中心人物约翰·马斯顿（精明的商人和专家猎人）以及其他人的两套新服装。</p><p>简体中文和繁体中文、韩语、波兰语、巴西葡萄牙语、俄语和拉丁美洲西班牙语等新语言与所有其他受支持的语言一起出现。此外，还有 PlayStation 4 的奖杯和 Nintendo Switch 上的游戏内成就。</p><p>最后， <em>《荒野大镖客：救赎》</em>的硬核模式已在 PlayStation 4 端口上解锁，玩家面临的挑战包括生命值减半、死眼瞄准无法自动填充、商店物品成本增加和售价降低等。 </p><figure id="attachment_3480339" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3480339" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3480339" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/red-dead-redemption-1-price-point-defended-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3480339" class="wp-caption-text"> 《荒野大镖客：救赎》来源：Take-Two Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> <em>Red Dead Redemption</em>现在可以在 PlayStation 4 和 Nintendo Switch 上以 39.99 英镑（49.99 美元）的价格购买数字版，实体版将于 10 月 13 日发售。</p><p>与 2021 年发布的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition"><em>《侠盗猎车手 3》、《侠盗猎车手：圣安地列斯》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto-the-trilogy-the-definitive-edition"><em>《侠盗猎车手：罪恶都市》</em></a>的重制版不同，新版本的<em>《荒野大镖客：救赎》</em>似乎对玩家来说运行相对可靠。</p><p> <a href="https://youtu.be/m9QmGxSKZ_4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Digital Foundry</em></a>对 PlayStation 4、PlayStation 4 Pro 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/playstation-5">PlayStation 5</a>上玩游戏体验的技术分析将其描述为“可用但非常保守的更新”。</p><p>结果发现，由于动画节奏问题，该游戏确实“在以 30 [帧/秒] 速度玩时感觉非常断断续续且有点断断续续”。虽然 Digital Foundry 承认这种情况不会一直发生，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/tags/xbox">Xbox</a>版本不会出现这个特殊问题。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/take-two-interactive">Take-Two Interactive</a>首席执行官 Strauss Zelnick 表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/red-dead-redemption-film-is-too-much-of-a-risk-suggests-publisher-3480504">，开发<em>《荒野大镖客：救赎》</em>电影或电视节目的财务风险太大</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/red-dead-redemption-has-launched-on-ps4-and-nintendo-switch-3484532">《Red Dead Redemption》的帖子已在 PS4 上发布，而 Nintendo Switch</a>则首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ;
绿日乐队宣布重新发行 30 周年纪念版《Dookie》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-massive-30th-anniversary-dookie-reissue-3484518?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=green-day-announce-massive-30th-anniversary- doookie重新发行Anagricel DuranThu, 17 Aug 2023 15:00:22 +0000 Music NewsNewsPunkRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3484518 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿日。图片来源：肯·施莱斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该版本将包含限量版套装，其中包含演示、剪辑等内容</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/green-day-announce-massive-30th-anniversary-dookie-reissue-3484518">绿日乐队宣布 30 周年纪念版《Dookie》重新发行的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="绿日。图片来源：肯·施莱斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day.-Credit-Ken-Schles-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>宣布将在下个月发行第三张录音室专辑《Dookie》，以纪念 30 周年纪念日。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/10-albums-that-wouldnt-exist-without-green-days-dookie-768209">如果没有 Green Day 的《Dookie》，这 10 张专辑就不会存在</a></strong></li></ul><p>为了庆祝 1994 年格莱美获奖专辑问世三十周年，《Dookie（30 周年豪华版）》将推出限量版六张 LP 黑胶唱片盒装、四张 CD 盒装，并将以数字形式提供。特别版的黑胶唱片——每张唱片都压在不同色调的棕色黑胶唱片上——将在 Green Day <a href="https://store.greenday.com/?psid=230203/gday/wr/ggl/na/br/GDWavoAlwaysOnSearch/s_hp/us/&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwivemBhBhEiwAJxNWN5YJiIgAQGdQTdo9a4_jLr7Y32PHkjMpjfXQwF3CVD4YoUD6qC3faRoCmJoQAvD_BwE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">网上商店</a>以及独立唱片店出售。</p><p>该合集收录了之前未发行的“Dookie”演示和片段，以及两首开创性的现场录音，“Live At Woodstock (1994)”（首次在 DSP 上）和之前未发行的“Live In Barcelona（1994 年 6 月 5 日）” 。查看下面的演示。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify Embed：Dookie（30 周年 4 首曲目演示）" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/4AFF6Md43PaWKv5lSMAysd?si=2PKovNsrTYO-YG93nt7EQQ&#038;nd=1&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>套装内装满了收藏品，包括一卷“Dookie”狗便便袋、五颗按钮套装、空气清新剂、明信片、保险杠贴纸、吻切大磁铁片、纸飞机、黑色和白色-白色<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">“</em>彩页<em style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;">”</em>封面平版插入，以及备用封面艺术的海报。</p><p> CD 盒套装包含两张贴纸、五按钮套装、空气清新剂和单个软乙烯基磁铁。两个盒装版本均配有格莱美奖获奖制作人罗布·卡瓦洛 (Rob Cavallo) 撰写的衷心个人介绍以及格莱美奖获得者鲍勃·梅尔 (Bob Mehr) 的详细内页注释。</p><p> 《Dookie (30 周年纪念豪华版) <em>》</em>将于 9 月 29 日发行。请<a href="https://greenday.lnk.to/dookie" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3484549" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3484549" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3484549" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1.jpg" alt="绿日“Dookie”彩色乙烯基压制品。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Green-Day-Dookie-Colored-Vinyl-Pressings.-Credit_-PRESS-1-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3484549" class="wp-caption-text">绿日“Dookie”彩色乙烯基压制品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“Dookie：30 周年豪华版”曲目列表为：</strong></h2><p><strong>乙烯基盒 (6LP)：</strong><br /> <strong>LP 1：《杜基》</strong><br /> <strong>LP 2：“Dookie 演示”</strong><br /> <strong>LP 3：“Dookie Outtakes”</strong><br /> <strong>LP 4：“伍德斯托克现场演出 (1994)”</strong><br /> <strong>LP 5 &amp; 6：“巴塞罗那现场演出（94 年 6 月 5 日）”</strong></p><p> <strong>CD盒（4CD）：</strong><br /> <strong>CD 1：《杜基》</strong><br /> <strong>CD 2：“Dookie 演示和片段”</strong><br /> <strong>CD 3：“伍德斯托克现