利兹音乐节加强安保以“清除”毒贩https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-steps-up-security-to-weed-out-drug-dealers-3484477?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=leeds-festival-steps-up-安全清除毒贩Liberty DunworthThu, 17 Aug 2023 13:57:28 +0000 FestivalsMusic NewsNewsReading & Leeds Festival.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3484477 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2022 年利兹音乐节" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>去年一名青少年在音乐节上死亡后，采取了更多措施</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-steps-up-security-to-weed-out-drug-dealers-3484477">利兹节后加强安全以“清除”毒贩的消息</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2022 年利兹音乐节" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/2022_LeedsFestivalCrowd_JasonRichardson-Alamy_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2022">雷丁和利兹</a>音乐节的组织者宣布，他们加强了安全措施，以“清除”在现场活动的毒贩。</p><p>一项调查获悉， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/teenage-boy-16-dies-after-suspected-consumption-of-ecstasy-tablet-at-leeds-festival-3299360">去年一名青少年在音乐节上死亡</a>后，采取了新措施。</p><p> 16 岁的大卫·塞利诺 (David Celino) 在参加 2022 年利兹音乐节的狂喜后病倒了，他的一群朋友从该网站 Camping Plus 区域的经销商处购买了音乐节。随后他被送往医院，并于8月28日去世。</p><p>在对儿子死亡的调查中，塞利诺的父亲詹皮耶罗表达了他的担忧，即音乐节对 18 岁以下的青少年来说并不安全，并敦促禁止 16 岁和 17 岁的青少年参加现场音乐活动。</p><p>现在，Festival Republic 的董事总经理梅尔文·本 (Melvin Benn) 向塞利诺的父母讲述了他在儿子去世后所感受到的“真正的悲伤”。 Speaking at the Wakefield Coroner&#39;s Court, he also revealed he had lost a nephew to drugs and explained that Celino&#39;s death had “taken an emotional toll on myself and all of my staff, no question about that” (via <a href="https://metro.co.uk/2023/08/17/festival-founder-says-teens-shouldnt-be-banned-despite-boys-ecstasy-death-19347010/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Metro</em></a> ).</p><p> He also confirmed that, while he does not think that under-18s should be banned, the festival will be introducing more security measures in this year&#39;s instalment. Particularly to protect teenagers from “predatory” drug dealers, who might take advantage of their “naivety”. </p><figure id="attachment_3300776" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3300776" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3300776" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1.jpg" alt="Leeds Festival main stage" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3300776" class="wp-caption-text"> Leeds Festival main stage. CREDIT: Katja Ogrin/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> These new measures include more security officials and support hubs on-site, and search dogs present at every entrance for 2023. Benn also told the court that organisers will be monitoring how many under-18s are attending the festival.</p><p> “[The festival] will operate a drugs operation aimed at weeding out dealers and having them removed from site, that&#39;s a very significant change,” he said (via <a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-leeds-66523003" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC News</em></a> ). “the intention is that no camper will be more than 200m from [a support hub],” he added.</p><p> Discussing the recent changes to the festival – which will be held from August 25 to 27 – Councillor James Gibson, chair of Leeds City Council&#39;s licensing committee, said that although he thinks it is “very unlikely” that the council could ban unaccompanied under-18s, he is “impressed” by the efforts to heighten security and crack down on drug dealers. </p><div class="ssrcss-11r1m41-RichTextComponentWrapper ep2nwvo0" data-component="text-block"><div class="ssrcss-7uxr49-RichTextContainer e5tfeyi1"> The inquest continues. </div></div><div class="ssrcss-xza2yt-ComponentWrapper ep2nwvo1" data-component="image-block"><div class="ssrcss-ab5fd8-StyledFigureContainer e34k3c21"></div></div><p> Last month, Reading and Leeds festival <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-replace-lewis-capaldi-reading-leeds-2023-3466700">confirmed that The 1975 will be the final headliners for this year&#39;s event</a> , following the withdrawal of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lewis-capaldi">Lewis Capaldi</a> .</p><p> Other headliners for this year&#39;s festival include <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foals">Foals</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/imagine-dragons">Imagine Dragons</a> . Other acts on the line-up include <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">Wet Leg</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bicep">Bicep</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/becky-hill">Becky Hill</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steve-lacy">Steve Lacy</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/muna">MUNA</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-snuts">The Snuts</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tion-wayne">Tion Wayne</a> and more.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-steps-up-security-to-weed-out-drug-dealers-3484477">Leeds Festival steps up security to “weed out” drug dealers</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
